A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:15PM on 27
January 2022. Inspector walked into the Sponsored Programs Administration Office and asked for a contact with the
IACUC, was provided contact information. Attempted to call and left a voicemail and sent an email, but the individual was
not on campus, remote working due to COVID.
End Section
